    summary: "Amazon Prime Day 2026 lifts off on June 23rd and will hopefully deliver the best deals of the summer. We’ve been covering the most notable pre-Prime Day discounts happening, and come next week, we’ll be bringing you many more deals — ones we can’t tell you about just yet. As usual, expect to see price [&#8230;]",
    body: "Amazon Prime Day 2026 lifts off on June 23rd and will hopefully deliver the best deals of the summer. We’ve been covering the most notable pre-Prime Day discounts happening, and come next week, we’ll be bringing you many more deals — ones we can’t tell you about just yet. As usual, expect to see price drops on a range of product categories, including smart home, headphones, smartwatches, monitors, 4K TVs, outdoorsy gear, and more.\n\nThe sale will conclude at 3:01AM ET on June 27th. We’ve put together this package so you can see all of our sprawling coverage in one convenient place. It contains not just our favorite one-off deals and category roundups to come, but also some shopping tips that might help you price-match purchases, and be the first to find amazing deals. The Echo Dot Max is cheaper than ever in an early Prime Day sale The best Apple deals you can already get ahead of Prime Day The best early Amazon Prime Day deals so far How to find the best deals during Amazon’s Prime Day sale Everything you need to know about Prime Day 2026 Nothing&#8217;s Ear (a), our favorite budget earbuds, are cheaper than ever ahead of Prime Day Amazon’s capable sound system is over $100 off ahead of Prime Day Amazon&#8217;s Smart Thermostat is on sale for just $58 My favorite Qi2 power bank is cheaper than ever for Verge readers Bose’s latest QuietComfort Ultra are $70 off, marking a new low price Here are the price-matching policies for Best Buy, GameStop, and others The AirPods Pro 3 are $179, their best-ever price Category Deals The best Apple deals you can already get ahead of Prime Day The best robot vacuum deals available ahead of Prime Day The best Prime Day deals under $50 Laptop prices suck these days, so here are some Prime Day deals that at least help a little Best Prime Day Charging Accessory Deals The best early Amazon Prime Day deals so far The best Prime Day deals we found on our favorite gear Breakout Tech Deals The Echo Dot Max is cheaper than ever in an early Prime Day sale The Nex Playground is down to its pre-RAMageddon price during Prime Day The Pixel 10A finally costs what it should Amazon’s Kindle Colorsoft bundle is almost half off for Prime Day Paramount Plus is two dollars for two months of ad-free viewing Nothing&#8217;s Ear (a), our favorite budget earbuds, are cheaper than ever ahead of Prime Day Amazon&#8217;s Smart Thermostat is on sale for just $58 My favorite Qi2 power bank is cheaper than ever for Verge readers Bose’s latest QuietComfort Ultra are $70 off, marking a new low price Amazon’s capable sound system is over $100 off ahead of Prime Day The AirPods Pro 3 are $179, their best-ever price News and Tips Amazon’s four-day Prime Day begins on June 23rd We’re giving away a Prime Day grab bag loaded with over $800 of free tech Here are the price-matching policies for Best Buy, GameStop, and others Everything you need to know about Prime Day 2026 How to find the best deals during Amazon’s Prime Day sale",
